{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"4202310b-49c4-4c53-9f73-dc8cf569c73f","content":"No repo-specific pipeline found, so here's the general migration guidance:\n\n## Migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform\n\n### 1. Update your test project\n\nIn your `.csproj`, add:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nEnsure you're on **MSTest 3.x+** (`Microsoft.Testing.Platform` is built in).\n\n### 2. Replace the pipeline task\n\n**Before (VSTest@3):**\n```yaml\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblies: '**/*Tests.dll'\n    resultsFolder: $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n```\n\n**After (`dotnet test`):**\n```yaml\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=TestResults.trx\"\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n### 3. Publish results & coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish TRX results'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish code coverage'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n### Key differences\n\n| | VSTest@3 | Microsoft.Testing.Platform |\n|---|---|---|\n| Runner | `vstest.console.exe` | Built into the test binary |\n| Task | `VSTest@3` | `DotNetCoreCLI@2` (command: test) |\n| TRX | Automatic | `--logger trx` |\n| Coverage | `codeCoverageEnabled` | `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` |\n\n> **Tip:** For Cobertura-format coverage (needed by `PublishCodeCoverageResults@2`), add the `coverlet.collector` NuGet package and use `--collect:\"XPlat Code Coverage\"` instead.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"4db57ab5-08b6-4050-b87c-ba8f740345ae","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The repository doesn't have relevant pipeline files. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge of migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform.","outputTokens":656,"requestId":"0832:204131:85D20BF:9402CAE:69EABE73"},"id":"8bdf00e0-6a2a-4194-bd1e-aec8d0c34ccc","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:51:12.858Z","parentId":"dc6b928b-9533-49a7-b7db-ba76842bb233"}
